| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0853 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ffa0d25e-924c-551c-8bcb-d3614a8e1ce6"
